    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1context_1_1RuntimeContextStorage" kindref="compound">RuntimeContextStorage</ref> is used by RuntimeContext to store Context frames.</para>
<para>Custom context management strategies can be implemented by deriving from this class and passing an initialized <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1context_1_1RuntimeContextStorage" kindref="compound">RuntimeContextStorage</ref> object to RuntimeContext::SetRuntimeContextStorage. </para>
